Maybe try to pip uninstall tensorflow first and pip3 install TF.

body:
I verified that gs is included in our builds. Maybe you're using the wrong version of tensorboard? You should use `pip3 install` for Python 3.

Maybe try to `pip uninstall tensorflow` first and `pip3 install` TF.

Closing because I manually verified gs paths work with the latest builds.
